tter.com%2Fmtrupdate%2Fstatus%2F1135413619674365952&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewONjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=bb619e55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmtrupdate%2Fstatus%2F1135413619674365952&h=d239bb93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mtrupdate/status/1135413619674365952</a><br />\n<br />\n顯著受阻即係要等20 mins <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"有車又趕人落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67fcb31c892408b67842f06af62520b3d3264ac","tid":1183613,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"<em></em>西鐵綫額外行車時間<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2019-06-03 13:12<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於錦上路站附近有信號故障，西鐵綫列車駛經荃灣西站和錦上路站路段時需要慢駛，西鐵綫來往紅磡站及屯門站的行車時間預計需要額外5-8分鐘。<br />\n西鐵綫服務更改如下<br />\n紅磡站 往返<br />\n屯門站<br />\n每10分鐘一班<br />\n現時西鐵綫月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長。<br />\n請為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\n港鐵職員現正進行搶修工作。<br />\n如有不便，敬請見諒。"},{"pid":"586a432f574fad705f1f1c8990361391ca020913","tid":1183613,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb56984a588dc0e86aa927fc6d0a31d88d699b3f","tid":1183613,"uid":19030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d737eee0deab84677be83772a3dfaa67d1c2e477","tid":1183613,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c25862ebed3a5b74375dd55d987317cc9405209","tid":1183613,"uid":102749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"慢慢等啦,狗鐵一定唔同你講要等幾耐<br />\n次次都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mtrupdate/status/1135413619674365952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmtrupdate%2Fstatus%2F1135413619674365952&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewONjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=bb619e55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmtrupdate%2Fstatus%2F1135413619674365952&h=d239bb